  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "你知道怎么给 AI 智能体高信号上下文吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.165,
      "spokenEnd": 2.743,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接下来我来告诉你，Anthropic 是怎么解决这个问题的。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.888,
      "audioStart": 2.747,
      "spokenStart": 2.903,
      "spokenEnd": 5.978,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.576,
      "audioStart": 5.921,
      "spokenStart": 6.078,
      "spokenEnd": 11.85,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic 把上下文看成有限的注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.24,
      "audioStart": 11.843,
      "spokenStart": 12.01,
      "spokenEnd": 14.435,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "窗口越满，真正重要的信号越容易被稀释。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 14.377,
      "spokenStart": 14.535,
      "spokenEnd": 17.336,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "提示词越长，AI 智能体越可能追着旧细节跑。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 17.335,
      "spokenStart": 17.496,
      "spokenEnd": 20.467,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "解决办法，是六部分高信号包：目标、规则、工具、示例、检索和状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 6.024,
      "audioStart": 20.413,
      "spokenStart": 20.567,
      "spokenEnd": 25.8,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "只保留当前约束和有效证据，目标就会重新变大。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.008,
      "audioStart": 25.797,
      "spokenStart": 25.96,
      "spokenEnd": 29.171,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "其他材料留在窗口外，需要时再检索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.24,
      "audioStart": 29.119,
      "spokenStart": 29.271,
      "spokenEnd": 31.712,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "核心判断只有一句：给 AI 智能体支持下一步行动的最小充分上下文，并随着任务持续更新。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.912,
      "audioStart": 31.715,
      "spokenStart": 31.872,
      "spokenEnd": 37.99,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先看注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 1.824,
      "audioStart": 38.011,
      "spokenStart": 38.17,
      "spokenEnd": 39.187,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会帮你判断，什么信息值得进入 AI 智能体的当前窗口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.704,
      "audioStart": 39.125,
      "spokenStart": 39.287,
      "spokenEnd": 43.204,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "上下文不只是提示词。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.232,
      "audioStart": 43.206,
      "spokenStart": 43.364,
      "spokenEnd": 44.801,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "系统指令、工具、示例、历史记录和当前请求，都会争夺同一份注意力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.712,
      "audioStart": 44.744,
      "spokenStart": 44.901,
      "spokenEnd": 49.816,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "材料越多，AI 智能体越难找回真正相关的信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.936,
      "audioStart": 49.824,
      "spokenStart": 49.976,
      "spokenEnd": 53.119,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "规则即使写进去了，也可能被旧计划和原始日志淹没。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.2,
      "audioStart": 53.058,
      "spokenStart": 53.219,
      "spokenEnd": 56.613,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每一步开始前，只问一个问题：什么信息会改变下一步判断？",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.584,
      "audioStart": 56.611,
      "spokenStart": 56.773,
      "spokenEnd": 60.569,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "保留目标、约束、证据和当前状态，其余内容只留索引。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.872,
      "audioStart": 60.506,
      "spokenStart": 60.669,
      "spokenEnd": 64.724,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "例如准备代码修改时，仓库规则和当前错误必须在窗口里；",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.632,
      "audioStart": 64.722,
      "spokenStart": 64.884,
      "spokenEnd": 68.703,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "完整日志可以只留路径。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.376,
      "audioStart": 68.64,
      "spokenStart": 68.803,
      "spokenEnd": 70.379,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最小充分不等于越短越好。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.592,
      "audioStart": 70.388,
      "spokenStart": 70.539,
      "spokenEnd": 72.336,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "验收条件、风险边界和必要证据，仍然必须完整。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.392,
      "audioStart": 72.272,
      "spokenStart": 72.436,
      "spokenEnd": 76.019,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "工具带来新证据后，要更新当前状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.192,
      "audioStart": 76.015,
      "spokenStart": 76.179,
      "spokenEnd": 78.58,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "用紧凑摘要替代已经完成使命的原始轨迹。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 78.512,
      "spokenStart": 78.68,
      "spokenEnd": 81.636,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，把上下文当作有限注意力预算。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.128,
      "audioStart": 81.635,
      "spokenStart": 81.796,
      "spokenEnd": 85.128,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，更多 token 不等于更强的信号。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 85.122,
      "spokenStart": 85.288,
      "spokenEnd": 87.459,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，随着任务变化，持续刷新上下文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 87.458,
      "spokenStart": 87.619,
      "spokenEnd": 90.288,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接下来提高输入质量。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.064,
      "audioStart": 90.316,
      "spokenStart": 90.468,
      "spokenEnd": 91.742,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章只讲三件最有用的事：指令、工具和示例。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.008,
      "audioStart": 91.681,
      "spokenStart": 91.842,
      "spokenEnd": 95.058,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "系统指令要明确目标、边界和判断原则。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.864,
      "audioStart": 95.063,
      "spokenStart": 95.218,
      "spokenEnd": 98.292,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "不要把所有分支写死，也不要只说“把事情做好”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.6,
      "audioStart": 98.229,
      "spokenStart": 98.392,
      "spokenEnd": 101.186,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "工具是 AI 智能体与环境的契约。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.928,
      "audioStart": 101.176,
      "spokenStart": 101.346,
      "spokenEnd": 103.469,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "名称、参数、错误和返回结果都要清楚，功能重叠的工具尽量合并。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.544,
      "audioStart": 103.402,
      "spokenStart": 103.569,
      "spokenEnd": 108.31,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果两个工具的边界连人都说不清，AI 智能体就更难稳定选择。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.04,
      "audioStart": 108.309,
      "spokenStart": 108.47,
      "spokenEnd": 112.723,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "示例不需要很多。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.776,
      "audioStart": 112.719,
      "spokenStart": 112.883,
      "spokenEnd": 113.874,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "两三个典型例子，展示主要模式和一条关键边界，通常比堆满例外更有效。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.904,
      "audioStart": 113.808,
      "spokenStart": 113.974,
      "spokenEnd": 119.08,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "判断一段信息是否值得保留，只看它能否改变结果、约束行为、选择工具或提供证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.816,
      "audioStart": 119.084,
      "spokenStart": 119.24,
      "spokenEnd": 125.249,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "高信号没有固定字数。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.232,
      "audioStart": 125.248,
      "spokenStart": 125.409,
      "spokenEnd": 126.824,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "只要信息承担了明确工作，它就值得保留。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.36,
      "audioStart": 126.76,
      "spokenStart": 126.924,
      "spokenEnd": 129.479,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，指令要清楚，但不要僵化。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.816,
      "audioStart": 129.48,
      "spokenStart": 129.639,
      "spokenEnd": 132.656,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，保留职责单一的最小工具集。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 132.652,
      "spokenStart": 132.816,
      "spokenEnd": 134.981,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用少量典型示例展示真正的模式。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.624,
      "audioStart": 134.981,
      "spokenStart": 135.141,
      "spokenEnd": 137.96,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在解决细节太多的问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.424,
      "audioStart": 137.986,
      "spokenStart": 138.14,
      "spokenEnd": 139.769,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会把“全部预加载”改成“需要时再打开”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.408,
      "audioStart": 139.709,
      "spokenStart": 139.869,
      "spokenEnd": 142.495,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "不要在任务开始前塞入所有文档。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.832,
      "audioStart": 142.498,
      "spokenStart": 142.655,
      "spokenEnd": 144.686,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "AI 智能体还没判断重点，注意力预算就已经被花掉了。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.272,
      "audioStart": 144.616,
      "spokenStart": 144.786,
      "spokenEnd": 148.236,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "上下文里先保留一张地图：文件路径、查询、链接和对象标识。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.688,
      "audioStart": 148.238,
      "spokenStart": 148.396,
      "spokenEnd": 153.304,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "真正需要证据时，再打开对应内容。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 153.24,
      "spokenStart": 153.404,
      "spokenEnd": 155.566,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "例如处理大仓库时，先搜索文件名，再读取目标片段，不要一次打开整个目录。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.88,
      "audioStart": 155.564,
      "spokenStart": 155.726,
      "spokenEnd": 160.809,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这就是渐进式披露。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 1.92,
      "audioStart": 160.802,
      "spokenStart": 160.969,
      "spokenEnd": 162.09,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "一次搜索缩小下一次搜索，AI 智能体只让正在使用的材料进入工作窗口。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 5.52,
      "audioStart": 162.017,
      "spokenStart": 162.19,
      "spokenEnd": 166.899,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最实用的是混合策略：稳定规则和当前目标预先加载，变化快、细节多的材料按需检索。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 7.272,
      "audioStart": 166.903,
      "spokenStart": 167.059,
      "spokenEnd": 173.534,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "按需检索会增加探索时间，所以路径命名、搜索工具和停止条件必须清楚。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 6.384,
      "audioStart": 173.53,
      "spokenStart": 173.694,
      "spokenEnd": 179.269,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，保留轻量引用，不预载全部正文。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.368,
      "audioStart": 179.269,
      "spokenStart": 179.429,
      "spokenEnd": 182.986,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，细节真正相关时再打开。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.88,
      "audioStart": 182.988,
      "spokenStart": 183.146,
      "spokenEnd": 185.236,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，在聚焦程度和检索成本之间做取舍。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 185.238,
      "spokenStart": 185.396,
      "spokenEnd": 188.357,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "长期任务还需要可恢复记忆。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.712,
      "audioStart": 188.376,
      "spokenStart": 188.537,
      "spokenEnd": 190.447,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会比较压缩、笔记和专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.288,
      "audioStart": 190.38,
      "spokenStart": 190.547,
      "spokenEnd": 193.028,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "窗口快满时，把轨迹压缩成连续性摘要。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.336,
      "audioStart": 193.031,
      "spokenStart": 193.188,
      "spokenEnd": 195.742,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "只带上决定、约束、证据、未决问题和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.368,
      "audioStart": 195.685,
      "spokenStart": 195.842,
      "spokenEnd": 199.407,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "压缩要先保证不漏关键信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.664,
      "audioStart": 199.403,
      "spokenStart": 199.567,
      "spokenEnd": 201.435,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "宁可多带一点，也不要丢掉后来无法恢复的约束。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.696,
      "audioStart": 201.376,
      "spokenStart": 201.535,
      "spokenEnd": 204.438,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "结构化笔记适合保存进度和工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.36,
      "audioStart": 204.446,
      "spokenStart": 204.598,
      "spokenEnd": 207.157,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "到达里程碑就更新笔记，用它替代冗长的原始历史。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.08,
      "audioStart": 207.099,
      "spokenStart": 207.257,
      "spokenEnd": 210.536,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "一份合格的交接摘要，必须保留目标、决定、证据、未知项和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.856,
      "audioStart": 210.536,
      "spokenStart": 210.696,
      "spokenEnd": 215.761,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "只有独立深挖的价值超过协调成本时，才使用专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.416,
      "audioStart": 215.751,
      "spokenStart": 215.921,
      "spokenEnd": 219.517,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "主 Agent 只接收压缩后的结论。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 2.688,
      "audioStart": 219.453,
      "spokenStart": 219.617,
      "spokenEnd": 221.505,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "持续对话适合压缩，有里程碑的工作适合笔记，独立研究才考虑专门 Agent。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.4,
      "audioStart": 221.501,
      "spokenStart": 221.665,
      "spokenEnd": 226.251,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，用高召回摘要压缩长轨迹。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.984,
      "audioStart": 226.252,
      "spokenStart": 226.411,
      "spokenEnd": 229.597,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，把持久状态写进结构化笔记。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.144,
      "audioStart": 229.6,
      "spokenStart": 229.757,
      "spokenEnd": 232.099,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，专门 Agent 只用于值得并行深挖的问题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.672,
      "audioStart": 232.098,
      "spokenStart": 232.259,
      "spokenEnd": 235.129,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后把方法装进一个可复用工具。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 2.856,
      "audioStart": 235.157,
      "spokenStart": 235.309,
      "spokenEnd": 237.355,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会完成六部分高信号上下文包。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 3.12,
      "audioStart": 237.295,
      "spokenStart": 237.455,
      "spokenEnd": 239.79,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
