      "id": "c06-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一组是结果目标和运行规则。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.736,
      "audioStart": 239.794,
      "spokenStart": 239.95,
      "spokenEnd": 241.901,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "写清交付物、验收条件、权限、风险边界和停止条件。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.92,
      "audioStart": 241.843,
      "spokenStart": 242.001,
      "spokenEnd": 246.116,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二组是工具地图和典型示例。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.952,
      "audioStart": 246.118,
      "spokenStart": 246.276,
      "spokenEnd": 248.437,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "说明工具何时使用，并用少量例子展示主要模式。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.104,
      "audioStart": 248.378,
      "spokenStart": 248.537,
      "spokenEnd": 251.837,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三组是检索索引和工作状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 2.832,
      "audioStart": 251.836,
      "spokenStart": 251.997,
      "spokenEnd": 254.022,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c06-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "记录证据入口、当前重点、关键决定、未知项和下一步动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.1,
      "audioDuration": 4.92,
      "audioStart": 253.97,
      "spokenStart": 254.122,
      "spokenEnd": 258.247,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.1
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "真正执行时，每个字段都要能回答一个问题：AI 智能体下一步该做什么？",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.4,
      "audioStart": 258.24,
      "spokenStart": 258.407,
      "spokenEnd": 263.006,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
