      "id": "c06-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：第一，用目标和规则锚定 AI 智能体。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 274.644,
      "spokenStart": 274.805,
      "spokenEnd": 278.061,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，用工具、示例和检索索引指导行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.816,
      "audioStart": 278.061,
      "spokenStart": 278.221,
      "spokenEnd": 281.228,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c06-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c06-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 5,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，用持续更新的工作状态保持连续性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 3.72,
      "audioStart": 281.23,
      "spokenStart": 281.388,
      "spokenEnd": 284.301,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "AI 智能体忘记重点，往往不是信息太少，而是没有区分的信息太多。",
      "gapBefore": 0.18,
      "audioDuration": 5.088,
      "audioStart": 284.322,
      "spokenStart": 284.481,
      "spokenEnd": 288.771,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.18
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，管理完整上下文，只保留会改变下一步判断的信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 4.464,
      "audioStart": 288.776,
      "spokenStart": 288.931,
      "spokenEnd": 292.61,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，提高信号质量，用清楚指令、最小工具集和典型示例指导行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.712,
      "audioStart": 292.615,
      "spokenStart": 292.77,
      "spokenEnd": 297.676,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，细节按需检索，长任务用压缩、笔记和工作状态保持连续性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.688,
      "audioStart": 297.678,
      "spokenStart": 297.836,
      "spokenEnd": 302.701,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
    {
      "id": "c07-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c07-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 6,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后带走六部分上下文包：目标、规则、工具、示例、检索和状态。",
      "gapBefore": 0.16,
      "audioDuration": 5.784,
      "audioStart": 302.71,
      "spokenStart": 302.861,
      "spokenEnd": 307.851,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.16
    },
